fulltext: John: Hey Halcyon! Come inside and say hi to the family!
Joe: Have you seen Kindred lately? I can't seem to find him anywhere...
Jeremy: What do you think is outside of this little box of a town?
Jonah: Why do all of our names start with a J? Seems a bit fishy don't you think?
Wait a second why doesn't your name start with a J!
Josh: Hey Halcyon! How are you doing today?
Jeremiah: You should stop by more often.. I hardly see you nowadays!
